        {
          "avatars": [
            {
              "id": "hoshina02",
              "action": "acknowledging",
              "expression": "happy",
              "attension": "true"
            }
          ],
          "location": "Park",
          "bgm": "main",
          "background": "park",
          "text": "'...I don't know what to do since this is so sudden, but let's start with being friends.'",
          "voice": "突然でどうしたら良いのかわからないのですが_とりあえずお友達からで"
